  <brief_title>Biochemical Marker to Predict the Recurrence of Atrial Fibrillation After Surgical Maze Procedure</brief_title>
  <official_title>Plasma ANP and NT-pro-BNP, Atrial Anatomical Change May Determine the Outcome of Maze Operation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
